    A personal learning notebook maintained by Manav Sehgal, written on an NVIDIA DGX Spark.
    Opinions expressed are the author's own, not those of any employer.
  </p>
  <div class="footer__bar">
    <div class="footer__links">
      <a href={base}>Home</a>
      <a href={`${base}stage/foundations/`}>Foundations</a>
      <a href={`${base}stage/inference/`}>Inference</a>
      <a href={`${base}stage/agentic/`}>Agentic</a>
      <a
        class="footer__icon"
        href="https://github.com/manavsehgal/ai-field-notes"
        rel="noopener"
        aria-label="ai-field-notes on GitHub"
      >
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path fill="currentColor" d="M12 .5C5.65.5.5 5.65.5 12a11.5 11.5 0 007.86 10.93c.58.11.79-.25.79-.55 0-.27-.01-1.18-.02-2.14-3.2.7-3.87-1.36-3.87-1.36-.52-1.33-1.27-1.69-1.27-1.69-1.04-.71.08-.69.08-.69 1.15.08 1.75 1.18 1.75 1.18 1.02 1.75 2.68 1.24 3.34.95.1-.74.4-1.24.72-1.53-2.55-.29-5.24-1.28-5.24-5.7 0-1.26.45-2.29 1.18-3.1-.12-.29-.51-1.46.11-3.05 0 0 .96-.31 3.15 1.18a10.95 10.95 0 015.74 0c2.19-1.49 3.15-1.18 3.15-1.18.63 1.59.23 2.76.11 3.05.74.81 1.18 1.84 1.18 3.1 0 4.43-2.69 5.41-5.25 5.69.41.36.78 1.06.78 2.14 0 1.55-.02 2.8-.02 3.18 0 .3.21.67.8.55A11.5 11.5 0 0023.5 12C23.5 5.65 18.35.5 12 .5z"/>
